{"tid":2133378,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特赦組織斥以言入罪","createTime":"2020-07-31T04:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T04:58:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad784753e7c882cd6fa90ab6bb69f7b466098bb","tid":2133378,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/KVA3GR2I3SI2B6V2TDF3FGOIS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FKVA3GR2I3SI2B6V2TDF3FGOIS4%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG17O6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=11389d87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FKVA3GR2I3SI2B6V2TDF3FGOIS4%2F&h=4ab6ed12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/KVA3GR2I3SI2B6V2TDF3FGOIS4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n特赦組織斥以言入罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】學生動源前召集人鍾翰林及三名前成員，前晚被警方國家安全處人員以涉嫌分裂國家及煽動他人分裂國家罪名上門拘捕，四人被通宵扣查後，至昨日未獲准保釋，正由律師跟進情況，據知警方已分別替各人錄口供。今次是港版國安法實施後，警隊國安處首次主動出擊拘捕，四人面臨最高刑罰是終身監禁。國際特赦組織香港分會直斥事件令香港產生寒蟬效應，議員亦炮轟當局針對學生，赤裸裸以言入罪。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：明言整頓教育界  清除「壞蘋果」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Wl8RW26u45aVr_ZCG11lX5ArLSM=/640x409/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5DH2ACYATNYJ34PKJ4ZNTWSKDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWl8RW26u45aVr_ZCG11lX5ArLSM%3D%2F640x409%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5DH2ACYATNYJ34PKJ4ZNTWSKDU.jpg&h=9173c091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n區議員：4學生搞分裂好無稽<br />\n<br />\n被捕三男一女（16至21歲），是學生動源前召集人鍾翰林及三名前成員，包括前發言人何諾恆、陳渭賢及鍾的女友何忻諾，各人報稱學生。前晚鍾被警方國安處人員上門拘捕，雙手。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方國安處高級警司李桂華前晚深夜見記者，指四人分別涉嫌觸。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據第20條，最。。。。。。。。。港社會產生寒蟬效應」。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議員王百羽直斥，警方「老屈四個學生有能力分裂國家，簡直無稽同可笑！」。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c380838f332016a5c1d7df8ffa1f429bf3ebb399","tid":2133378,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"First they came for 民族黨，I did not speak out<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2133341\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2133341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}